name: Froggy Swing!
description:
Made for the itch.io Mini Jam 106 Frogs²!

Click towards objects to grab them with your tongue, hold mouse button down to hold on, your tongue will pull you in! Release mouse to let go!

Swing the most distance as possible within the time limit! Beat your own hi-score or post it below in the comments for others to beat!

Programming & Sounds: Me!
Art: My lovely girlfriend!
Music: "Moe Moe Garden in the Brain" Royalty Free Music
